{"word":"καταναλίσκω","slug":"καταναλίσκω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>καταναλίσκω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-ανᾱλώσω</el>) (aor1 <el>-ηνάλωσα</el>) (<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, aor1 <el>-ανᾱλωθῆναι</el>) </el><p/><i>to use up, spend, lavish</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, with <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a>, <i>to be lavished</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/>"}]}